### Waste Location Products API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

### 1. Basic request - Get products from location
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": 123
}

### 2. Test with different location ID
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": 456
}

### 3. Test missing locationId (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 4. Test invalid locationId type (should handle gracefully)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": "invalid"
}

### 5. Test with zero locationId
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": 0
}

### 6. Production endpoint (change URL as needed)
POST https://your-production-domain.com/api/waste/location-products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": 123
}
